OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FKinship carers, including
OL,8,Fgrandparents, aunts, uncles and family
OL,9,Ffriends who step in to provide care
OL,10,Ffor children, will now be paid under a
OL,11,Fnew government scheme.
OL,13,FSeveral councils already pay kinship
OL,14,Fcarers, but the Department for
OL,15,FEducation has announced that it will
OL,16,Flaunch the largest investment in
OL,17,Fsupport for such carers nationally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThe pilot scheme will run for up to
OL,8,Fthree and a half years, and will begin
OL,9,Fin seven areas of the country known as
OL,10,FKinship Zones.
OL,12,FITV News previously reported on
OL,13,Fkinship carers, who are are often
OL,14,Fgiven just 24 hours to decide if they
OL,15,Fcan become the carer of a loved one's
OL,16,Fchild - but unlike parents, they are
OL,17,Fnot entitled to parental leave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThe latest statistics from the care
OL,8,Fcharity Kinship reveal that the
OL,9,Fabsence of parental leave has
OL,10,Fcompelled thousands of kinship carers
OL,11,Fto leave their jobs and rely on
OL,12,Fbenefits.
OL,14,FFour in 10 are forced to claim
OL,15,Fbenefits or increase their benefits,
OL,16,Faccording to the survey and 45% of
OL,17,Fthose in work lose their jobs or
OL,18,Fcareers when taking on the care of a
OL,19,Fchild.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
