CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FStatistics show that the lack of
OL,8,Fparental leave means thousands of
OL,9,Fkinship carers are being forced to
OL,10,Fquit their jobs and claim benefits, as
OL,11,FITV News' Digital Political Reporter,
OL,12,FLewis Denison, reports
OL,14,FAreas that will fall under the Kinship
OL,15,FZones are Bexley in Greater London,
OL,16,FBolton, Newcastle, North East
OL,17,FLincolnshire, Medway, Thurrock and
OL,18,FWiltshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThe department said around 5,000
OL,8,Fvulnerable children and their families
OL,9,Fcould be helped by the pilot, which is
OL,10,Fbacked by a #126 million investment.
OL,12,FBut national kinship care charity
OL,13,FKinship said the pilot will cover only
OL,14,Fa small fraction of children in
OL,15,Fkinship care across England and
OL,16,Fcautioned that while it is an
OL,17,Fimportant first step, more is needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
