PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FParents and adoptive parents in the UK
OL,8,Fare entitled to up to 52 weeks off
OL,9,Fwork, which can be split between mums
OL,10,Fand dads, but kinship carers get none.
OL,12,FThe vast majority of kinship carers
OL,13,Ftake on a child under five.
OL,15,FAs children do not usually start full-
OL,16,Ftime education until the September
OL,17,Fafter their fourth birthday, many
OL,18,Fcarers receive little daytime respite
OL,19,Fbefore school begins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FChildren and families minister Josh
OL,8,FMacAlister said: "As a country we owe
OL,9,Fkinship carers our thanks and our
OL,10,Fsupport, and the new financial
OL,11,Fallowance which we're trialling as
OL,12,Fpart of our plan for change recognises
OL,13,Fthe vital role they play ensuring
OL,14,Ffamilies can stay together.
OL,16,F"We promised to introduce this scheme
OL,17,Fto support kinship carers who step up
OL,18,Ffor the children they love and give
OL,19,Fevery child the best possible start in
OL,20,Flife.
OL,26,@pD@ROUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"These Kinship Zones will lead the way
OL,8,Fin showing the impact for children
OL,9,Fwhen we unlock the power of
OL,10,Fgrandparents, aunts, uncles and other
OL,11,Frelatives who could care for their kin
OL,12,Fin the place of the care system."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
