CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FDr Jo Casebourne, chief executive of
OL,8,Fthe government-funded Foundations,
OL,9,Fwhich works to help vulnerable
OL,10,Fchildren, said her organisation is
OL,11,F"pleased to undertake the evaluation
OL,12,Fof the kinship financial allowances
OL,13,Fpilot announced today, to help to
OL,14,Fbuild the evidence base and shape
OL,15,Ffuture support for kinship carers and
OL,16,Fthe children they care for".
OL,26,@sD@AOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FJahnine Davis, who is the national
OL,8,Fkinship care ambassador, said the
OL,9,Fpilot is a "milestone" for kinship
OL,10,Fcarers and the children they care for,
OL,11,Fwhich means "for the first time, we
OL,12,Fhave a governmentled initiative that
OL,13,Fwill not only examine how best to
OL,14,Fprovide financial support for kinship
OL,15,Ffamilies but will also encourage local
OL,16,Fauthorities to look holistically at
OL,17,Fthe support they offer and adopt a
OL,18,Fgenuine 'think family' approach."
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@VO]sD@MOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FKinship chief executive Lucy Peake
OL,8,Fsaid: "While it's welcome that this
OL,9,Fsupport is being piloted in a small
OL,10,Fnumber of local authorities to build
OL,11,Fthe evidence for further roll-out, the
OL,12,Fpace of change remains far too slow,
OL,13,Fwith the pilot reaching only around 4%
OL,14,Fof children in kinship care in England.
OL,16,F"Most families will see no change,
OL,17,Fcontinuing to face a postcode lottery
OL,18,Fof poor and inconsistent support.
OL,19,FWhile the pilot is positive for those
OL,20,Fincluded, it risks paralysing progress
OL,21,Felsewhere."
OL,26,@pD@GOUxD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FShe said local authorities should not
OL,8,Fwait until the end of the pilot, but
OL,9,Finstead "follow the lead of the small
OL,10,Fnumber of areas already seeing the
OL,11,Fbenefits of equal allowances to
OL,12,Ffamilies and their budgets".
OL,14,FThe charity said that for every 100
OL,15,Fchildren looked after in well-
OL,16,Fsupported kinship care rather than
OL,17,Flocal authority care, the state saves
OL,18,F#4 million per year and increases the
OL,19,Flifetime earnings of those children by
OL,20,F#2 million.
OL,26,@qD@IOUtD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThere are over 141,000 children in
OL,8,Fkinship care in the UK.
OL,10,FThe charity Kinship said not only are
OL,11,Fcarers saving the government money by
OL,12,Fkeeping the youngsters out of the care
OL,13,Fsystem, but they are also helping them
OL,14,Fgrow into successful adults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772186488
OL,3,CKinship carers in England to receive
OL,4,Cfinancial support under 'milestone'
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FMunira Wilson, the Liberal Democrats'
OL,8,Fspokesperson on education, children
OL,9,Fand young people, said: "While this
OL,10,Fpilot is a welcome step in the right
OL,11,Fdirection, it is a drop in the ocean,
OL,12,Fwith over 130,000 kinship carers
OL,13,Facross England, many left without any
OL,14,Ffinancial support to care for their
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,F"The Liberal Democrats will continue
OL,18,Fto fight for all kinship families to
OL,19,Freceive financial support on a par
OL,20,Fwith foster carers and a right to paid
OL,21,Femployment leave."
OL,26,@qD@YOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
